items.description:
Defines a set of properties that can be used to describe an action. 

The properties are:

- `type`: optional, allows a string value;
- `title`: optional, allows a string value;
- `body`: optional, allows a string value;
- `at`: optional, allows a string value;

This interface is designed to provide a structure for actions that require additional information beyond just the type of action. The presence or absence of these properties can be controlled by using optional types.
